TITLE: Creating a Custom Dagger Module for Google Cloud Run Deployment in Python
DESCRIPTION: This Python code snippet creates a custom Dagger module that uses the google-cloud-run module to deploy an application to Google Cloud Run. It defines a 'deploy' function that takes project details, image information, and credentials as inputs.
