TITLE: Defining Tekton Pipeline for Dagger Integration
DESCRIPTION: YAML configuration for a Tekton Pipeline that integrates Git repository cloning with a Dagger pipeline execution. The pipeline includes two tasks: git-clone and a custom dagger task.
SOURCE: https://github.com/dagger/dagger.git/blob/main/docs/current_docs/ci/integrations/tekton.mdx#2025-04-16_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: yaml
CODE:
```
apiVersion: tekton.dev/v1beta1
kind: Pipeline
metadata:
  name: git-pipeline
spec:
  params:
    - name: git-url
      type: string
    - name: dagger-cloud-token
      type: string
      default: ""
  workspaces:
    - name: source
  tasks:
    - name: clone
      taskRef:
        name: git-clone
      params:
      - name: url
        value: $(params.git-url)
      workspaces:
        - name: output
          workspace: source
    - name: read
      runAfter: ["clone"]
      taskRef:
        name: dagger
      params:
        - name: dagger-cloud-token
          value: $(params.dagger-cloud-token)
      workspaces:
        - name: source
          workspace: source
```

