TITLE: Visualizing Dagger Session Interface (DSI) Basic Flow with Mermaid Sequence Diagram
DESCRIPTION: This Mermaid sequence diagram illustrates the basic flow of the Dagger Session Interface (DSI). It shows the interactions between 'dagger run', localhost, SDK, and runner components, including the process of starting a runner, establishing connections, and executing GraphQL queries.
SOURCE: https://github.com/dagger/dagger.git/blob/main/core/docs/d7yxc-operator_manual.md#2025-04-16_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: mermaid
CODE:
