TITLE: Changelog Entry v0.6.4
DESCRIPTION: Lists additions including directory and file sync features, container focus controls, and host directory copying improvements.
SOURCE: https://github.com/dagger/dagger.git/blob/main/CHANGELOG.md#2025-04-16_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: markdown
CODE:
```
## v0.6.4 - 2023-07-19

### Added
- cli: show total duration at the end of a run
- engine: add `Directory.Sync`
- engine: add `File.Sync`
- engine: add `Container.WithFocus` & `Container.WithoutFocus`
- engine: add `include` & `exclude` to host dir copy name

### Deprecated
- engine: deprecate `exitCode`

### Fixed
- engine: prevent session id from busting caches everywhere
- engine: optimize `WithDirectory` & `WithFile` via MergeOp
- engine: remove unimplemented git fields
- engine: support optionally setting explicit OCI mediatypes
```

