SOURCE: https://github.com/dagger/dagger.git/blob/main/sdk/rust/crates/dagger-sdk/examples/existing-dockerfile/app/README.md#2025-04-16_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
npm install
```

----------------------------------------

TITLE: Running JavaScript Build Script
DESCRIPTION: Command to execute the JavaScript build pipeline.
SOURCE: https://github.com/dagger/dagger.git/blob/main/sdk/rust/crates/dagger-sdk/examples/caching/app/README.md#2025-04-16_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
node ./build.js
```

----------------------------------------

TITLE: Dagger Version Warning
DESCRIPTION: Exception for handling version compatibility warnings in Dagger
SOURCE: https://github.com/dagger/dagger.git/blob/main/sdk/python/docs/exceptions.rst#2025-04-16_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: python
CODE:
```
class VersionMismatch(Warning)
```
